Exscript
---------
Exscript is a scripting/template language for automating Telnet
and SSH sessions.


Installation
-------------
Extract the archive and you are ready to start the interpreter:

  ./exscript --help

Provides an overview over command line options. For example Exscript
programs, have a look into the lib/Exscript/tests/ directory.

More information can be found on the project homepage:
http://code.google.com/p/exscript/


Requirements
-------------
Python >= 2.2
Python-crypto
python-pexpect
ssh
